textDisplay: @Mark Humphreys  This razor is a cartridge razor and they tend to give irritation and ingrown hairs buy a safety razor and some DE blades and a decent soap and shaving brush. you will spend a little in the beginning but save a lot in the end as 100 blades cost as little as $12  and a soap will last upward of 6 months . If you need help getting put in the right direction come check out the facebook group Shave the Man  ! lots of gents that can  give you info on a good beginner setup :)
textOriginal: @Mark Humphreys  This razor is a cartridge razor and they tend to give irritation and ingrown hairs buy a safety razor and some DE blades and a decent soap and shaving brush. you will spend a little in the beginning but save a lot in the end as 100 blades cost as little as $12  and a soap will last upward of 6 months . If you need help getting put in the right direction come check out the facebook group Shave the Man  ! lots of gents that can  give you info on a good beginner setup :)
